      "review_summary": "The PR adds a hidden-diagnostic callback to tool planning, preserves plugin-authored availability metadata in plugin tool descriptors, and logs unsupported availability diagnostics during plugin tool resolution.\n\nPR surface: Source +254, Tests +305. Total +559 across 10 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection of PR head shows a valid shared child expression is rejected because the same WeakSet is reused across sibling branches, and current main source also reproduces the original silent hidden-diagnostic behavior.",
      "review_followup": "- [P2] A narrow automated repair can fix the recursion-stack bug and add focused regression coverage, while the final canonical PR choice remains maintainer-owned.",
      "freeform_prompt": null,
